# Modern browsers that support ES2020+ features
# This eliminates the need for most polyfills

Chrome >= 80
Firefox >= 72
Safari >= 14
Edge >= 80
iOS >= 14
Android >= 80

# No IE support - saves significant bundle size
not IE 11
not IE_Mob 11

# Exclude very old browsers
not Chrome < 80
not Firefox < 72
not Safari < 14
not Edge < 80

# Production browsers
[production]
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions
not dead
not IE 11

# Development browsers
[development]
last 1 Chrome version
last 1 Firefox version
last 1 Safari version
last 1 Edge version